# Restaurant Inventory Operations System

A workflow-based restaurant inventory and operational tracking system designed to automate inventory monitoring, waste logging, stock movement tracking, and low-stock visibility for small and medium-sized food businesses.

---

## Overview

This project is built to streamline restaurant inventory operations through modular workflow automation and centralized stock monitoring.

The system currently focuses on:

- Inventory tracking
- Waste management
- Stock movement logging
- Low-stock monitoring
- Employee operational input
- Webhook-based process automation

The architecture is designed to be scalable for future operational modules and integrations.

---

## Core Features

- Stock-in workflow automation
- Waste tracking system
- Inventory movement logging
- Real-time stock querying
- Low-stock monitoring
- Employee operations terminal
- Webhook-based backend processing
- Modular workflow architecture
- Operational response dashboard

---

## Supported Operations

### STOCK_IN
Adds inventory quantities and records stock movement logs.

### WASTE
Deducts spoiled or wasted inventory items while maintaining movement history.

### QUERY_STOCK
Checks the current stock level of a specific ingredient.

### QUERY_LOW
Displays all ingredients currently below or equal to minimum stock threshold.

